---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Episode #404: Page Not Found">
  <article class="max-w-5xl">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-stone-400 mb-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">The Nexus</span>
        <span>&middot;</span>
        <span>#404</span>
        <span>&middot;</span>
        <time>February 30, 2014</time>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Page Not Found</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-stone-300 text-lg">
        The lost episode. We definitely recorded this one, but it seems to have
        slipped into a parallel dimension. Some say it contained the secret to
        infinite battery life. Others say it was just Ryan talking about CSS for
        forty minutes. We may never know.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-8 text-sm">
      <div>
        <span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-stone-400">Hosts:</span>{" "}
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-stone-300">The Usual Suspects</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-stone-400">Duration:</span>{" "}
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-stone-300">∞:∞:∞</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-8 p-4 bg-amber-50 dark:bg-amber-950 border border-amber-200 dark:border-amber-800 rounded-lg text-sm text-amber-900 dark:text-amber-200">
      <p>
        <strong>Transmission Error:</strong> The page you're looking for doesn't
        exist or has been lost to the technological convergence. It may have been
        moved, deleted, or perhaps it never existed in the first place.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a
        href="/"
        class="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors"
      >
        Go Home
      </a>
      <a
        href="/episodes/"
        class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 dark:border-stone-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-stone-300 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-stone-800 transition-colors"
      >
        Browse Episodes
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>
